@startuml agent-deck-mcp-architecture

title MCP 服务器 — 顶层架构概览 (5 大块 + 跨切组件)

' 节点名用日常术语优先,括号注 codename
' 详细 module 名 / 函数名 / LOC / commit / REVIEW 引用见 INDEX 第 3 列「关联 plan / commit」

package "入口" as L1 {
  [tool 入口 (15 tools)\nstdio + HTTP /mcp] as Entry
}

package "权限拦截" as L2 {
  [入口拦截器\n(withMcpGuard + 白名单)] as Guard
}

package "tool 实现" as L3 {
  [tool handler facade\n(15 tools 按功能分组)] as Handler
  [业务实现层\n(impl + 公共助手)] as Impl
}

package "持久层" as L4 {
  [4 张数据表\n(会话 / 团队 / 消息 / 任务)] as Repos
  database "SQLite 数据库" as DB
}

package "运行时联动" as L5 {
  [会话管理器\n(生命周期 + spawn-link)] as SM
  [adapter + SDK 子进程\n(claude + codex)] as Adapter
  [消息派发轮询器\n(250ms poll)] as Watcher
}

' ─── 主调用链 ───
Entry --> Guard : 每个 tool 调用先过白名单
Guard --> Handler : 通过后分发到 15 tool facade
Handler --> Impl : facade → impl 业务实现
Handler --> Repos : 读写 4 张数据表
Impl --> Repos
Impl --> SM : 起 / 关 / 改 session lifecycle
SM --> Adapter : 起 SDK 子进程 + emit event
Handler --> Watcher : send_message 入队 → watcher dispatch
Watcher --> Adapter : 把消息喂给 receiver SDK
Repos --> DB

' ─── 专题子图 cross-ref (画图人按主题查) ───

note bottom of Handler
  专题子图(深入看实施细节):
  - **archive-plan** 收口流程: archive-plan-architecture + archive-plan-state-machine
  - **hand-off-session** 接力: hand-off-session-architecture + hand-off-session-state-machine
  - **sdk-bridge** 双端: sdk-bridge-architecture + sdk-bridge-state-machine
  - **消息派发**: universal-message-status-state-machine
end note

note bottom of Repos
  术语对照: sessionRepo=会话表 / agentDeckTeamRepo=团队表
  / agentDeckMessageRepo=消息表 / taskRepo=任务表
end note

